    "--- \n",
    "\n",
    "### Question 1e\n",
    "\n",
    "In addition to being regressive, how did the property tax system in Cook County place a disproportionate tax burden on non-white property owners?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Property owners could appeal the property tax, but this required time, money (to hire a tax attorney), and understanding of the appeal system. Because of this, most non-white property owners were not able to appeal while most white property owners were. Because of this, white property owners were able to get lower property tax while non-white property owners were not."
   ]
